    <br>At Gib John Tutoring, we are committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, and safeguard your personal information when you visit our website, use our tutoring services, or engage with us in other ways. By accessing or using our website and services, you agree to the terms of this Privacy Policy.

